    "en": {
      "title": "14 students were the targets of wasp stings",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "14 students and two teachers studying at Basara Tamil National School were targeted by Kulavikot.",
        "A total of 16 students, including 14 students and two teachers in grades 1 and 2, were bitten by wasps and were admitted to Pasara General Hospital for treatment.",
        "The incident took place today (18) at around 11.00 am and the wasp nest in the school premises attacked the students and teachers."
      ],
